<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179335>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Histogram of egg length of the two Huffmanela species parasitic in Gymnocranius grandoculis. JNC 892: eggs from the gills, syntypes of H. filamentosa Justine, 2004. JNC 1726, JNC 2166, JNC 2174, eggs of H. lata n. sp. JNC 1726: eggs from the mesentery. JNC 2166 and JNC 2174: eggs from the swimbladder." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179335/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

